<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about FixMySpine's mission to connect Australians with trusted allied health professionals. Discover our story from a North Sydney clinic to a nationwide directory.">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/dist.css?v=7">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-background">
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="bg-white shadow-md fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary">
                        FixMySpine
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:block">
                    <div class="ml-10 flex items-baseline space-x-4">
                        <a href="/" class="text-text hover:text-primary px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">Home</a>
                        <a href="/about" class="text-primary px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium border-b-2 border-primary">About</a>
                        <a href="/pricing" class="text-text hover:text-primary px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">Pricing</a>
                        <a href="/contact" class="text-text hover:text-primary px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">Contact</a>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn-primary">List Your Practice</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-bg pt-32 pb-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">
                Our Mission: Connecting Australians with Trusted Allied Health Professionals
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-white/90">
                Building on a legacy of excellence to serve communities nationwide
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            
            <!-- Our Story -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Story</h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
                        FixMySpine began as a trusted name in North Sydney, where for years we served the local community as a reputable allied health clinic. Our practitioners built strong relationships with patients, earning a reputation for quality care, professionalism, and genuine commitment to helping people achieve better health outcomes.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
                        That legacy of trust wasn't something we wanted to keep confined to one suburb. We realised that Australians across the country deserve access to the same level of quality and transparency when searching for allied health professionals. Too often, people struggle to find reliable information about chiropractors, physiotherapists, osteopaths, and other practitioners in their area.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
                        So we evolved. FixMySpine transformed from a single clinic into something much bigger—a comprehensive, curated directory designed to connect Australians with verified, quality healthcare professionals throughout the nation. We've taken the trust and standards we built in North Sydney and expanded them to create a platform that serves the entire Australian community.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Mission -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Providing Transparency</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            Real patient reviews and detailed practitioner profiles help you make informed decisions about your healthcare.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Ensuring Quality</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We carefully curate our directory, working only with licensed, professional practitioners who meet our standards.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Supporting Practitioners</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We give quality healthcare providers the tools and visibility they need to grow their practices and help more patients.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Building Community</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            By connecting patients and practitioners across Australia, we're creating a healthier, more informed community.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- What We Offer -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">What We Offer</h2>
                
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">For Patients</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-text">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Comprehensive search by location and specialty</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Verified practitioner profiles with qualifications</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Authentic patient reviews and ratings</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Easy comparison of practitioners and services</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">For Practitioners</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-text">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Professional listing with detailed profile options</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Enhanced visibility through premium features</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Patient inquiry management tools</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Analytics to track profile performance</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Values -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Values</h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Trust & Integrity</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We maintain the highest standards of honesty and transparency in everything we do. Our reputation was built on trust, and we protect it fiercely.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Quality Over Quantity</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We carefully curate our directory to ensure every practitioner meets our professional standards. It's not about having the most listings—it's about having the right ones.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Patient-Centered</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            Your health and wellbeing come first. Every feature we build and decision we make is guided by what's best for patients seeking quality care.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Australian Focus</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We understand the unique needs of Australian healthcare consumers and practitioners, and we're committed to serving our local communities with excellence.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <div class="bg-primary rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-4">
                    Join Our Growing Community
                </h2>
                <p class="text-white/90 text-lg mb-6">
                    Whether you're looking for care or looking to grow your practice, FixMySpine is here to help.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                    <a href="/search" class="btn-accent">
                        Start Your Search
                    </a>
                    <a href="/register" class="btn-secondary">
                        List Your Practice
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-text text-white py-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">FixMySpine</h3>
                    <p class="text-white/80">
                        Connecting Australians with trusted healthcare professionals.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Company</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="/about" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">About Us</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/contact" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Contact</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/pricing" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Pricing</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">For Practitioners</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="/register" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Register</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/login" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Login</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/dashboard" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Dashboard</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Legal</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="/terms-of-service" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Terms of Service</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-white/20 mt-8 pt-8 text-center">
                <p class="text-white/80">&copy; 2024 FixMySpine. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

